channel.title: Webclients Rspscoding
channel.description:
Rspscoding.org hosts free Webclient as many of you shall know, but how do i connect my .jar file to rspscoding, is it just a simple download link? or? I don't know, i tried a megaupload link on their and nothing, Somebody help me (:
Thanks for reading
- Dale x

item.title: Webclients Rspscoding
item.dc:creator: @Tutorial Tutorial
item.description:
@Tutorial wrote:

You have to be using a direct file host such as FileDen. You can even create a free webs account, upload the jar to there, and then post the link on the rspscoding site. Bam you are good to go.
